{"paragraphs":[{"cues":[{"time":2000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":93000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":104000,"text":"I'm Jon M. Chu. And I'm not a dancer,"},{"time":107000,"text":"I'm not a choreographer -- I'm actually a filmmaker, a storyteller."},{"time":111000,"text":"I directed a movie two years ago"},{"time":113000,"text":"called \"Step Up 2: The Streets.\""},{"time":115000,"text":"Anybody? Anybody? Yeah!"},{"time":117000,"text":"During that movie I got to meet a ton of hip-hop dancers --"},{"time":119000,"text":"amazing, the best in the world --"},{"time":121000,"text":"and they brought me into a society, the sort of underground"},{"time":124000,"text":"street culture that blew my mind."},{"time":126000,"text":"I mean, this is literally human beings"},{"time":128000,"text":"with super-human strength and abilities."},{"time":131000,"text":"They could fly in the air. They could bend their elbow all the way back."},{"time":133000,"text":"They could spin on their heads for 80 times in a row."},{"time":136000,"text":"I'd never seen anything like that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":138000,"text":"When I was growing up, my heroes were people like"},{"time":140000,"text":"Fred Astaire, Gene Kelly, Michael Jackson."},{"time":144000,"text":"I grew up in a musical family."},{"time":146000,"text":"(Laughter)"},{"time":147000,"text":"And those guys, those were like, ultimate heroes."},{"time":150000,"text":"Being a shy, little, skinny Asian kid growing up in the Silicon Valley"},{"time":153000,"text":"with low self-esteem, those guys made me believe in something bigger."},{"time":156000,"text":"Those guys made me want to, like, \"I'm going to do that"},{"time":158000,"text":"moonwalk at that bar mitzvah tonight for that girl.\""}]},{"cues":[{"time":161000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":164000,"text":"And it seems like those dance heroes have disappeared,"},{"time":167000,"text":"sort of relegated to the background of pop stars and music videos."},{"time":171000,"text":"But after seeing what I've seen,"},{"time":173000,"text":"the truth is, they have not disappeared at all."},{"time":175000,"text":"They're here, getting better and better every day."},{"time":178000,"text":"And dance has progressed."},{"time":180000,"text":"It is insane what dance is right now."},{"time":182000,"text":"Dance has never had a better friend than technology."}]},{"cues":[{"time":184000,"text":"Online videos and social networking ..."},{"time":186000,"text":"dancers have created a whole global laboratory online"},{"time":189000,"text":"for dance, where kids in Japan are taking moves"},{"time":191000,"text":"from a YouTube video created in Detroit,"},{"time":193000,"text":"building on it within days and releasing a new video,"},{"time":196000,"text":"while teenagers in California are taking the Japanese video and remixing it"},{"time":198000,"text":"with a Philly flair to create a whole new dance style in itself."},{"time":202000,"text":"And this is happening every day."}]},{"cues":[{"time":204000,"text":"And from these bedrooms and living rooms and garages,"},{"time":207000,"text":"with cheap webcams,"},{"time":209000,"text":"lies the world's great dancers of tomorrow."},{"time":211000,"text":"Our Fred Astaires, our Gene Kellys"},{"time":213000,"text":"our Michael Jacksons are right at our fingertips,"},{"time":215000,"text":"and may not have that opportunity, except for us."}]},{"cues":[{"time":218000,"text":"So, we created the LXD,"},{"time":220000,"text":"sort of a -- the Legion of Extraordinary Dancers,"},{"time":223000,"text":"a justice league of dancers that believe"},{"time":225000,"text":"that dance can have a transformative effect on the world."},{"time":227000,"text":"A living, breathing comic book series,"},{"time":230000,"text":"but unlike Spiderman and Iron Man,"},{"time":232000,"text":"these guys can actually do it."},{"time":234000,"text":"And we're going to show you some today. So, let me introduce to you,"},{"time":236000,"text":"some of our heroes right now."},{"time":238000,"text":"We got Madd Chadd,"},{"time":240000,"text":"Lil' C, Kid David and J Smooth."},{"time":243000,"text":"Please be excited, have fun, yell, scream."},{"time":245000,"text":"Ladies and gentlemen: The LXD."}]},{"cues":[{"time":247000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":248000,"text":"(Video): Madd Chadd: When people first see me,"},{"time":250000,"text":"I get a lot of different reactions actually."},{"time":254000,"text":"Sometimes you would think that maybe kids would enjoy it,"},{"time":258000,"text":"but sometimes they get a little freaked out."},{"time":262000,"text":"And, I don't know, I kind of get a kick out of that a little bit."}]},{"cues":[{"time":266000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":342000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":347000,"text":"J Smooth: When I'm in the zone -- I'm dancing and free styling it --"},{"time":350000,"text":"I actually visually kind of picture"},{"time":353000,"text":"lines, and moving them."},{"time":355000,"text":"I think of like, Transformers,"},{"time":357000,"text":"like how panels open and then they fold,"},{"time":361000,"text":"they fold in, and then you close that panel."},{"time":364000,"text":"And then another thing opens,"},{"time":367000,"text":"you close that."}]},{"cues":[{"time":369000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":445000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":451000,"text":"Kid David: It's kind of like, honestly a lot of times"},{"time":453000,"text":"I don't really know what's going on"},{"time":455000,"text":"when I'm dancing."},{"time":457000,"text":"Because at that point it's just really like, it's my body and the music."},{"time":459000,"text":"It's not really a conscious decision,"},{"time":461000,"text":"\"I'm going to do this next, I'm going to do this.\""},{"time":464000,"text":"It's kind of like this other level"},{"time":467000,"text":"where you can't make choices anymore,"},{"time":469000,"text":"and it's just your body reacting to certain sounds in the music."},{"time":473000,"text":"I got my name just because I was so young."},{"time":475000,"text":"I was young when I started. I was younger than a lot of the people I was dancing with."},{"time":479000,"text":"So, it was always like, they called me Kid David, because I was the kid."}]},{"cues":[{"time":486000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":534000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":541000,"text":"L'il C: I tell them to create a ball,"},{"time":543000,"text":"and then you just use that ball of energy."},{"time":545000,"text":"And instead of throwing it out, people would think"},{"time":547000,"text":"that's a krump move, that's a krump move."},{"time":549000,"text":"That's not a krump move. You're going to throw it out,"},{"time":551000,"text":"you throw it out, and you hold it."},{"time":553000,"text":"And you let it go, and then right when you see the tail,"},{"time":555000,"text":"you grab it by the tail, then you bring it back in."},{"time":557000,"text":"And you just got this piece of energy"},{"time":560000,"text":"and you just, you're manipulating it."},{"time":562000,"text":"You know, you create power, then you tame it."}]},{"cues":[{"time":570000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":636000,"text":"(Applause)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":648000,"text":"(Music)"}]},{"cues":[{"time":990000,"text":"(Applause)"}]}]}